        <item>
            <title>【現場評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 現埸實試　新焦段+輕巧+畫質媲美第一代 G Master</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機測試]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony G]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220886</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 推出新 G 系列鏡頭 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，屬於全新焦段，同時繼續輕巧的設計，放上 A7CII 的機身上感覺平衡。小編就參與了 Sony 的「試鏡」活動，以下同大家分享在會場的試用感受，事不宜遲，馬上實測！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220896 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220899 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sony 推出新 G 系列鏡頭 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>新鏡新焦段，長度輕巧適中</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 屬 Sony 鏡頭羣的全新焦段，新鏡造得更輕，只重 440 克，兼且有 F2.8 大光圈，更加有利低光時表現。新鏡鏡筒長 92.3mm，拎出街攝影或者放入相機袋，整體體積適中。配合 FX3、A7C 等細機時，機身與鏡頭的平衡也不俗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220897 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220908 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整體體積適中，機身與鏡頭的平衡也不俗</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MTF 曲線，畫質媲美第一代 G Master</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 用上了 4 片非球面鏡及 2 片的 ED 超低色散鏡片有效地減少像差，亦以最佳方式抑制色差。FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，Sony 就提供了純淨的散景波波。波波裡面的洋葱圈效果降得更加更加低。新鏡最近對焦距離達 1:3，24mm 時有 0.19mm，50mm 時有 0.30mm。最大放大倍率 0.3 倍。 MTF 曲線顯示，FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 畫質可媲美第一代 G Master，在記者會中我們未能詳細測試這方面，日後有機會再為鏡頭作深入評測。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220904 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220905 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220903 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MTF 曲線顯示，FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 畫質可媲美第一代 G Master</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/sony-ps5-slim-digital/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Slim + 光碟機開箱，安裝示範 + 香港價錢 + 發售日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/10/test-sony-16-35mm-f2-8-gm-ii-lens/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony FE 16-35mm F2.8 GM II 廣角變焦鏡頭，邊緣成像超清 + 對焦準繩度高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/sony-and-honda-ev-venture-to-launch-suv-and-compact-before-2030/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony、Honda 合資電動車品牌   Afeela 將添加 SUV 和小型車款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>兩線性摩打驅動，支援 120fps 高速連拍</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 內部對焦系統由兩個線性摩打驅動，可寧靜迅速地自動對焦。在寂靜地方拍攝影片，都不用擔心將摩打噪音收錄到影片中。新鏡能夠配合最新的 A9III 拍攝 120fps 相片，亦支援 Dynamic Active 動態主動或 Avtive Mode 主動模式影像穩定功能，及相容於相機的對焦呼吸補償功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220906 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220909 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220916 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 內部對焦系統由兩個線性摩打驅動，可寧靜迅速地自動對焦</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>操控具拍片特性</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 顧及了拍片的使用者，包括有光圈環及光圈點擊開關，可選擇 1/3 級，AF/MF 切換按鈕及直接控制光圈。無段光圈環最重要是拍攝影片時，可順滑地調整影片的景深，配合變焦焦點改變，可製造出極具創意的影像效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220907 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220910 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220911 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 顧及了拍片的使用者，有光圈環及光圈點擊開關切換按鈕及直接控制光圈，及 AF/MF 切換按鈕及直接控制光圈</p><h2></h2><h2>香港價格、供應</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">建議零售價：HK$8,990</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">預售日期：2024 年 2 月 27 日至 4 月 24 日</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">預計取貨日期：2024 年 4 月 26 日起</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">預售地點：Sony Online Store，Sony 專門店，特約零售商</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">預售優惠：送多層鍍膜保護濾鏡 VF-67MPAM/2 SYH（價值 HK$530）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220917 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220918 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220920 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220922 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220923 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220924 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/sony-ps5-slim-digital/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Slim + 光碟機開箱，安裝示範 + 香港價錢 + 發售日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/10/test-sony-16-35mm-f2-8-gm-ii-lens/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony FE 16-35mm F2.8 GM II 廣角變焦鏡頭，邊緣成像超清 + 對焦準繩度高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/sony-and-honda-ev-venture-to-launch-suv-and-compact-before-2030/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony、Honda 合資電動車品牌   Afeela 將添加 SUV 和小型車款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/">【現場評測】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 現埸實試　新焦段+輕巧+畫質媲美第一代 G Master</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
